description: This file is a header (.h) file defining function prototypes for the HTTP Ato FxCat2 Object, including creation, removal, and initialization functions used within the HTTP module of a BroadWay Service Delivery System. It contains import guards, license information, module descriptions, and function prototypes.

methods.name: HttpCreateAtoFxCat2
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Http Ato FxCat2 object, accepting container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat2Create
methods.description: Initializes and creates the Http Ato FxCat2 object, accepting container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat2Remove
methods.description: Removes or deallocates the Http Ato FxCat2 object.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat2EnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the Http Ato FxCat2 instance.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat2Initialize
methods.description: Initializes the Http Ato FxCat2 object.
